name: Soapbox - Immersive Entertainment
summary: Soapbox brings an intimate and up-close next-generation concert experience into your living room with music artists filmed in immersive 360 video. These true-life volumetric videos feature life-size holograms of real-time performances rendered in AR (live in your room) or VR (live in a fully rendered world). Get up close and personal and see your favorite musicians live from every angle. No avatars, no CGI, just the most lifelike music experience ever, only from Soapbox.
